<h2>Choice of Programming Languages</h2>

<b>What is the most suitable programming language?<br>

Answers:<br>

(  ) the client wants X, therefore X is the most suitable<br>

(  ) the computer system dictates X, therefore X is the most suitable<br>

(  ) cost/benefit analysis indicates X is the most suitable<br>
     ("risk" can be translated into "cost")
